---
title: Nectarine and Cucumber Panzanella with Mint, Arugula and Fresh Mozzarella
description: What’s not to like about a salad that’s equal parts bread and veggies? This crisp, crunchy and juicy panzanella gets its gusto from baguette slices, zucchini ribbons, fresh mozzarella and nectarine slices!
